data.description: This 4-bedroom, 2-bath home is nestled within a pristine master-planned community and offers modern living in a newly constructed space. Built in 2020, this residence embodies contemporary design and provides a comfortable and spacious living environment. The home features an attractive facade with a blend of architectural elements, showcasing clean lines and a welcoming entrance. The master bedroom includes an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet, providing a private retreat for the homeowners. The other three bedrooms are well-suited for family members or guests, with generous closet space. Energy-efficient HVAC and insulation to maintain a comfortable indoor climate year-round. This home, situated in a master-planned community, offers a combination of modern amenities, aesthetic appeal, and functional design, making it a perfect space for a family to live, grow, and create lasting memories. Schedule your private showing today.
